        "source_node_type": "gene",
        "target_node_type": "disease",
        "properties": {
          "ResearchMethod": {
            "type": "String",
            "values": [
              "The criteria used in prioritizing genes included (i) fine-mapped T1D coding variants in the gene, (ii) relevant phenotype when the gene is perturbed in an animal or human cell model system, and (iii) fine-mapped T1D non-coding variants with regulatory links to the gene."
