              "strong evidence based on biology only, with a phenotype in a relevant animal or cell perturbation model",
              "strong evidence based on both genetics and biology, with (i) phenotype in a relevant animal or cell perturbation model and (ii) epigenome and/or QTL link to T1D variant",
